The paper discusses the problem of content-based image retrieval, which involves using visual content to identify relevant images. This topic falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also mentions the use of machine learning techniques (cs.MM, cs.DL) and evaluation of algorithms (cs.LG). Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely to be associated with this paper.
